""
JINJA 2
It is used to make dynamic html pages ,
It is a template engine in flask used to show python values inside html , and
It is only work in html

Examples -
1- python values
{{variable }}
{{name}}

<p>Welcome {{name}}</p>
2- conditionals
is_topper =True

{% if is_topper%}

<p>You are a topper </p>
{% else %}
<p>You need to work hard </p>
{% endif %}
""
""q
Template inheritance -
It define a base layout in html and we can use it to all html pages , which helps to reduce code duplicating 
Layout set - 
Defining a common page structure that all pages will follow.
Dynamic Content -
content that changes based on data, user, or logic

""
""
Always remember to end the tag % end % ,otherwise server error
%extends% - tells Jinja2:
This page is a child template and should use another template as its layout.
%block% -a placeholder area in a parent (layout) template
that child templates can replace or fill.

